Found this place while looking for a non-chain restaurant in Anthem.
They had good fresh food, beer specials and excellent service.
Cody was our server and it is rare to see someone his age with such a great work ethic- it was refreshing!
I'd recommend checking it out if your looking to break out of the city for a night!

